                                                <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                    <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">ATMS BMS FEATURES</h2>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d6538d2 pb20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="d6538d2" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;_animation_mobile&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
                                                <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                    <p>The AMP BMS Architecture is highly flexible, <br />configurable, and scalable. Engineered to <br />accelerate development, our <a href="https://www.amp.tech/lp-battery-management-system/">battery management system</a> for EV utilizes <br />proprietary software to meet your unique <br />requirements.</p>
                                                    <ul>
                                                        <li>Scalable for Configurations (Single &amp; Multi Strings)</li>
                                                        <li>Available for 24V to 1000V Applications</li>
                                                        <li>Solid State up to 400A</li>
                                                        <li>ASIL C Safety Rated</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-dfbf745 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-html" data-id="dfbf745" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="html.default">
